(firstQuint)Sun May Arise on SMA : Newborn Screening of SMA in Belgium.

 The aim of this project is to demonstrate the feasibility, and the medico-economic impact of a SMA neonatal screening in an European country.

 We propose a 3-year-neonatal screening program in Southern Belgium (Federation Wallonie-Bruxelles, FWB) where there is 59.

000 newborns/year, among whom 6 are affected by spinal muscular atrophy.

